{
  "name": "OneFlare - Cloudflare WAF Web-Attack Response (SQLi / XSS / Traversal)",
  "description": "Alert-triggered SOAR playbook covering the three Cloudflare WAF ML web-application detections on the soledrop.co zone: CF-WAF-SQLi, CF-WAF-XSS, and CF-WAF-Traversal (one parametrized workflow; trigger matches alert name contains 'CF-WAF-'). Flow: extract offending src_ip + alert context -> parallel enrichment (S1 PowerQuery for other CF security events from the same IP + VirusTotal IP reputation) -> decision gate (VT malicious OR >3 correlated events) -> BLOCK the src_ip at Cloudflare (zone IP Access rule) + add S1 IOC on a confirmed verdict, else non-destructive managed CHALLENGE -> annotate the alert, raise the analyst verdict, and notify SOC via Slack + email. run_automatically:false (analyst-approved). Destructive block is gated on a threat-intel/correlation verdict per evidence discipline.",
